---
export const prerender = true;
import ServiceLayout from "../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<ServiceLayout
    title="Insight Processing"
    subtitle="Experience Counts. Building a Specialist Team in Your Mortgage Broking Practice."
    logoImage="/images/logo-insight-processing-brown.png"
    heroImage="/images/insight-processing-hero-v2.png"
    features={[
        "100% Australian Based",
        "Deep Industry Knowledge",
        "Full Loan Cycle Support",
        "Seamless Integration",
        "Aggregator Agnostic",
    ]}
>
    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <div class="space-y-8 animate-on-scroll">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            In 2006, Insight Processing identified a need to assist the finance
            professional in improving the overall profitability of their
            mortgage finance broking business. Like most financial transactions,
            mortgage finance is often a complex process, requiring regular
            contact with both the borrower client and the lender.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Removing the back office headache, client follow up, gathering
            outstanding documents and keeping the borrower client and broker
            informed electronically and personally throughout the process
            eliminates a time-consuming business task. This takes pressure from
            all parties by an administration professional who is entirely
            conversant with lender procedures and understands the demands of the
            finance professional.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Outsource Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-primary">Why Outsource?</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div
                class="bg-surface p-6 border border-subtle/20 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
            >
                <Icon
                    name="mdi:chart-line-variant"
                    class="w-10 h-10 text-accent mb-4"
                />
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Enhance Efficiency</h3>
                <p class="text-subtle mb-4">
                    Build a specialist team in your practice. Focus on
                    high-impact work while we handle the processing.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div
                class="bg-surface p-6 border border-subtle/20 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
            >
                <Icon
                    name="mdi:cash-multiple"
                    class="w-10 h-10 text-accent mb-4"
                />
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Boost Profitability</h3>
                <p class="text-subtle mb-4">
                    Delegating back-office work can streamline operations,
                    reduce costs, and enhance client satisfaction.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div
                class="bg-surface p-6 border border-subtle/20 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
            >
                <Icon
                    name="mdi:clock-check-outline"
                    class="w-10 h-10 text-accent mb-4"
                />
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Save Time</h3>
                <p class="text-subtle mb-4">
                    Free up your time for revenue-generating activities.
                    Outsource the top 5 time-consuming tasks.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div
                class="bg-surface p-6 border border-subtle/20 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
            >
                <Icon
                    name="mdi:account-group"
                    class="w-10 h-10 text-accent mb-4"
                />
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Experience Counts</h3>
                <p class="text-subtle mb-4">
                    Since 2006, our 100% Australian-based team has been
                    supporting brokers with deep local lending knowledge.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Cost Effective Solution -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-primary/5 p-8 rounded-xl animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">
            A Cost Effective Business Solution
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            When one assesses how much time is taken in the processing side of a
            loan transaction versus the interview and advice side, we can
            demonstrate that the “hourly chargeable rate” of the broker is 2 to
            3 times higher if they focus on advice.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Put simply, the cost of our processing centre is far less than the
            cost of the broker or their admin team. Even better, the efficiency
            through Insight Processing is far greater, leading to a very happy
            borrower client.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Services & Pricing -->
    <div class="mt-20 animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-primary">
            Our Services & Pricing
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Service 1 -->
            <div
                class="bg-surface border border-subtle/20 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg flex flex-col"
            >
                <div class="bg-primary p-6 text-main">
                    <h3
                        class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/90"
                    >
                        Submission Service
                    </h3>
                    <div class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2 text-white">
                        A$50 - A$220
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col">
                    <p class="font-bold mb-4">
                        Most popular: Data Entry & Submission ($220)
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 flex-1 pl-0 ml-0 list-none">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:check"
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-1"
                            /> Doc collection
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:check"
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-1"
                            /> Servicing data entry
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:check"
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-1"
                            /> Urgent submission options
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a
                        href="/contact"
                        class="block text-center py-2 px-4 border border-primary text-primary font-bold hover:bg-primary hover:text-main transition-colors rounded"
                        >Enquire</a
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 2 -->
            <div
                class="bg-surface border-2 border-accent rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl transform scale-105 z-10 flex flex-col"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-accent text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 uppercase tracking-wider"
                >
                    Popular
                </div>
                <div class="bg-primary p-6 text-main">
                    <h3
                        class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/90"
                    >
                        Loan Processing
                    </h3>
                    <div class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2 text-white">
                        A$75 - A$290
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col">
                    <p class="font-bold mb-4">
                        From receipt of submission to settlement
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 flex-1 pl-0 ml-0 list-none">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:check"
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-1"
                            /> Land and Construction
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:check"
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-1"
                            /> Top-ups / Increases
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:check"
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-1"
                            /> Commercial applications
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:check"
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-1"
                            /> Equipment finance
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a
                        href="/contact"
                        class="block text-center py-3 px-4 bg-accent text-white font-bold hover:bg-accent/90 transition-colors rounded"
                        >Enquire Now</a
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 3 -->
            <div
                class="bg-surface border border-subtle/20 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg flex flex-col"
            >
                <div class="bg-primary p-6 text-main">
                    <h3
                        class="text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/90"
                    >
                        Admin Support
                    </h3>
                    <div class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2 text-white">
                        A$280 - A$1000
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col">
                    <p class="font-bold mb-4">
                        Project based & ongoing support
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 flex-1 pl-0 ml-0 list-none">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:check"
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-1"
                            /> Custom admin packages
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:check"
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-1"
                            /> Outside scope of processing
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:check"
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-1"
                            /> Loan tracking support
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a
                        href="/contact"
                        class="block text-center py-2 px-4 border border-primary text-primary font-bold hover:bg-primary hover:text-main transition-colors rounded"
                        >Enquire</a
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <div class="mt-20 animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-primary">
            What Our Clients Say
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <blockquote
                class="bg-surface p-8 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-accent shadow-sm"
            >
                <div class="flex text-accent mb-4">
                    <Icon
                        name="mdi:format-quote-open"
                        class="w-8 h-8 opacity-50"
                    />
                </div>
                <p class="italic text-subtle mb-6">
                    "Shannon's thorough knowledge of Banking products and
                    processes, along with her attention to detail helps see our
                    client's loans approved and settled in a timely manner. I
                    feel confident in the knowledge that my lending files are
                    being actioned correctly."
                </p>
                <cite class="not-italic font-bold block text-primary"
                    >— Stephen, Mortgage Broker (Sydney)</cite
                >
                <span class="text-sm text-subtle">With Insight for 8 years</span
                >
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote
                class="bg-surface p-8 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-accent shadow-sm"
            >
                <div class="flex text-accent mb-4">
                    <Icon
                        name="mdi:format-quote-open"
                        class="w-8 h-8 opacity-50"
                    />
                </div>
                <p class="italic text-subtle mb-6">
                    "I have been extremely happy with Vicki and Insight
                    Processing. Having her behind the scenes chasing up
                    documents and checking on settlements saves me a lot of time
                    and worry on every loan I submit, which also allows me to
                    focus on converting more of my leads. It's a win win."
                </p>
                <cite class="not-italic font-bold block text-primary"
                    >— Peter, Mortgage Broker (Victoria)</cite
                >
                <span class="text-sm text-subtle">With Insight for 4 years</span
                >
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="mt-20 animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-primary">
            Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <details
                class="group bg-surface rounded-lg border border-subtle/20 overflow-hidden"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold lg:text-lg cursor-pointer p-6 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <span>What are your fees?</span>
                    <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                        <Icon name="mdi:chevron-down" class="w-6 h-6" />
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-subtle">
                    We offer a very competitive fee structure offering
                    processing only or the full service, including Full
                    Submission. Contact us to discuss your requirements so that
                    we may tailor a programme to meet your business needs.
                </div>
            </details>
            <details
                class="group bg-surface rounded-lg border border-subtle/20 overflow-hidden"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold lg:text-lg cursor-pointer p-6 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <span>Will I deal with one processor or several?</span>
                    <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                        <Icon name="mdi:chevron-down" class="w-6 h-6" />
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-subtle">
                    We match you and your files with a particular processor, and
                    that processor will be your contact. Continuity is
                    essential, and we always strive to meet your expectations.
                </div>
            </details>
            <details
                class="group bg-surface rounded-lg border border-subtle/20 overflow-hidden"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold lg:text-lg cursor-pointer p-6 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <span
                        >Is it faster to use Insight to get deals settled?</span
                    >
                    <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                        <Icon name="mdi:chevron-down" class="w-6 h-6" />
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-subtle">
                    Yes. Due to the volume being processed, we have developed
                    unique relationships with lenders. They know our staff, and
                    we meet with the lenders regularly to explore ways to
                    improve the shared process.
                </div>
            </details>
            <details
                class="group bg-surface rounded-lg border border-subtle/20 overflow-hidden"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold lg:text-lg cursor-pointer p-6 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <span>What lenders do you deal with?</span>
                    <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                        <Icon name="mdi:chevron-down" class="w-6 h-6" />
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-subtle">
                    We process deals with all lenders.
                </div>
            </details>
            <details
                class="group bg-surface rounded-lg border border-subtle/20 overflow-hidden"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold lg:text-lg cursor-pointer p-6 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <span
                        >Do I still contact my client throughout the process?</span
                    >
                    <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                        <Icon name="mdi:chevron-down" class="w-6 h-6" />
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-subtle">
                    This will be your call whether you want to make the client
                    contact. In our experience, your client is only too happy to
                    be in direct contact with us.
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</ServiceLayout>

<script>
    import { gsap } from "gsap";
    import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";

    gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

    const elements = document.querySelectorAll(".animate-on-scroll");

    elements.forEach((element) => {
        gsap.fromTo(
            element,
            {
                y: 50,
                opacity: 0,
            },
            {
                y: 0,
                opacity: 1,
                duration: 1,
                ease: "power3.out",
                scrollTrigger: {
                    trigger: element,
                    start: "top 80%",
                    toggleActions: "play none none reverse",
                },
            },
        );
    });
</script>
